    <item>
      <title>一张照片就能让你开心吗？我们询问了摄影师，这是他们发给我们的照片</title>
      <link>https://npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2024/03/19/1239277032/can-a-picture-make-you-happy-we-asked-photographers-and-heres-what-they-sent-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在国际幸福日，摄影师给我们发来了一些照片，其中有叙利亚男孩在照顾农场动物中找到乐趣、乌克兰女孩在蹦床上、音乐爱好者在布鲁斯音乐中嬉戏等等。]]></description>
      <guid>https://npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2024/03/19/1239277032/can-a-picture-make-you-happy-we-asked-photographers-and-heres-what-they-sent-us</guid>
